ï»¿

The object of the game is to collect clusters of 3 or more matching, adjacent symbols to win a prize.

When 3 or more identical symbols are connected by 1 side in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize, and the connected symbols are removed from the grid and replaced with new symbols. Wild symbols can help create clusters.

The Expander Spider Symbol expands the grid based on revealed arrow patterns and performs its action when no more winning clusters remain.

The game continues until no winning clusters remain on the grid.

Collect 3 Bonus Symbols to trigger the Bonus Game.

Bonus Game
Click the pumpkins to reveal Candy Symbols, Instant Win Symbols, or Multiplier Symbols.
Collect Candy Symbols to populate the meters. Fill a meter to win a prize.
Wild Candy Symbol adds one to each meter.
Find a Mystery Potion Symbol to reveal an Instant Win prize.
Reveal a Skull Cookie Symbol to multiply the Bonus Win amount.

What spooky riches can you unearth from the misty graveyard? Play Emoti Collect Halloween Super Spin and find out! Spin the wheel and collect Emoti Symbols to fill the meters and win prizes. Play on if you dare!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Each game starts with 6 spins of the wheel â€“ hit the â€œPlayâ€ button for each spin, or hit the â€œFast Forwardâ€ button to automatically play through all 6 spins.

At the end of each spin, all Emoti Symbols in the center segment are highlighted and added to the prize meter. Spins continue until there are 0 spins remaining.

Emoti Symbols are multiplied by the Multiplier value (1x, 2x, or 3x) in the center segment and added to the prize meter.

If a Pumpkin Symbol lands in the center segment, choose 1 Pumpkin to win a prize instantly. Up to 3 Pumpkins may appear as a result of landing on a Pumpkin Symbol. On subsequent spins, if the Pumpkin Symbol appears again, there is 1 fewer Pumpkin to choose from.

If a Spider Symbol appears, the center segment expands from 3 Emoti Symbols to 5 Emoti Symbols and additional Emoti Symbols are added to the prize meter. The center segment resets on the next spin.

If an Extra Spin Symbol appears, additional spins are awarded.

Collect 5 Bonus Ghost Symbols to trigger the Spooky Bonus.

Spooky Bonus
The bonus begins with 3 turns.

If a Bonus Ghost Symbol appears on a turn, the symbol locks in place on the grid and the counter resets to 3 turns.

Win a prize when 4 or more Bonus Ghost Symbols lock in place on the grid.

The bonus ends when 0 turns remain or the play grid fills with 16 Bonus Ghost Symbols.

Completing the Game
The game ends after all wheel spins in the base game and any triggered bonus games have completed.

Auto Play
Press the double-arrow/fast-forward button to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections have been made.

Instant Win Symbols

Medusa Coin symbols may also appear in the Respins Bonus and the Free Turns Bonus.

Respins Bonus
When a Double Snake symbol lands on the grid, it triggers the Respins Bonus.
The Double Snake symbol transforms into another symbol and locks into place. Any matching symbols that land on the grid turn to gold and lock into place for the duration of the bonus.
The remaining symbols spin. Any symbols that land and match the current gold symbols also turn to gold and lock into place.
If the grid fills completely with Medusa Coin symbols (Instant Win symbol), the progressive jackpot is awarded.
The Respins Bonus ends when there are no more symbol matches, or the jackpot is awarded.

Free Turns Bonus
The Free Turns Bonus is triggered when 3 Bonus Symbols appear in the grid. Triggering the bonus awards 5 initial free turns and a 1x multiplier.
Before the bonus begins, a pick screen appears with 15 Mystery tiles. Pick each tile to reveal additional free turns, additional multipliers, or to start the bonus.
Once the Begin Bonus icon is revealed, the bonus starts. Any additional turns awarded in the pick screen are applied during the bonus, up to 15 total free turns.
Gameplay in the Free Turns Bonus is similar to the base game - match 5 or more symbols anywhere to win a prize.
Medusa Coin symbols may appear and award instant prizes.
The Double Snake symbol may appear in the Free Turns Bonus and trigger the Respins Bonus.
All prizes awarded during the Free Turns Bonus are multiplied by the total multiplier value from the pick screen, up to a total of 5x.
The Free Turns Bonus ends when all turns have been played.

Completing the Game
The game ends when there are no more matches in the base game and any triggered bonus games have completed.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Match 3, 4, or 5 of the same symbols across a row to win a prize. The game contains 6 rows, each played individually.
Reveal the symbols of each row manually or by pressing the play button.
The 4th and 5th symbol of each row are revealed by a spinning symbol. Wild Symbols can appear in the 4th and 5th columns. The Wild Symbol substitutes for all symbols, except Coin Symbols and Magic Carpet Symbols, which trigger bonus games.

Palace Plinko Bonus
Trigger the Palace Plinko Bonus by collecting 5 or more Coin Symbols across all rows.
The Palace Plinko Bonus features a coin pusher machine. Drop coins into the machine by tapping the slots above the coins. Coins pushed off the edge award prizes.
The number of Coin Symbols collected in the base game determines how many coins can be dropped in the bonus game.
The bonus ends once all coins have dropped, and no additional coins remain to fall off the edge.

Magic Carpet Picker Bonus
Trigger the Magic Carpet Picker Bonus by revealing the Magic Carpet Symbol.
Select magic carpets to reveal symbols. Reveal a Magic Lamp Symbol to win a prize. Reveal a double Magic Lamp Symbol to win double the prize. Reveal a triple Magic Lamp Symbol to triple the prize.
The bonus ends once all magic carpets have been revealed.

Completing the Game
The game ends when all symbols have been revealed in the base game and any triggered bonus games have completed.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Reveal an Instant Win Symbol to instantly win a multiple of your bet. Available Instant Win prizes are 1x, 2x, 5x, 10x, 20x, and 50x the bet.
Reveal a Prize Multiplier Symbol to multiply the prize win amount. Available Prize Multipliers are 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x, and 10x.

Free Turns Bonus
Trigger the Free Turns Bonus when 3 Bonus Symbols appear anywhere on the grid during the base game.
The Free Turns Bonus awards 5 free turns.
Gameplay is the same as the base game.
Instant Win Multiplier Symbols and Prize Multiplier Symbols are available in the Free Turns Bonus.

Completing the Game
The game ends when all symbols have been flipped and any triggered bonus games have completed.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Collect clusters of matching, adjacent symbols to win prizes.
When 3 or more identical symbols are connected and share a side in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize and is removed from the grid.
Additional symbols cascade down to fill the grid. These symbols can create new clusters, which award prizes and are removed from the grid. This process continues until no new clusters form.
The game continues until no winning clusters remain on the grid and all prizes have been awarded.
If triggered, the Progressive Jackpot amount is awarded in lieu of any other prizes.

Wild Symbols
Wild Symbols can substitute for all cluster symbols. Wild Symbols can help create or enhance clusters, but only apply when they are part of a winning cluster.

Match Anywhere Feature
The Match Anywhere feature can award instant win prizes or the progressive jackpot.
If 3 or more of the Gold Hammer symbols appear anywhere on the grid, the corresponding prize shown in the meter is awarded after all clusters have been evaluated.
The Gold Hammer symbols remain in view on the grid once they appear.

Free Turns Bonus
Get 9 free turns when 3 Bonus Symbols appear anywhere on the grid.
Game play in the bonus is similar to the base game, where each turn may create winning clusters with matching symbols.
Level Up Feature
During the bonus, any Gold Hammer symbols that appear are collected in the meter. Once the meter is filled, the Match Anywhere prizes increase, except for the progressive jackpot. Prizes can increase a maximum of 3 times.
+1 Free Turn Symbol
When a +1 Turn Symbol appears in the bonus, it awards an extra turn. If multiple +1 Turn Symbols appear, the total number of extra turns awarded is equal to the number of +1 Turn Symbols.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no clusters remain on the grid and any bonus games are completed.

Immerse yourself in the treasures hidden beneath the waves in Reef Riches! Match a cluster of 3 to 8 symbols to win a prize! You might even hook a progressive Hot Hits Jackpot Bonus prize from the depths!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of the game is to collect clusters of 3 or more matching adjacent symbols to win a prize. The game displays a 5x3 symbol grid.
Press BUY to start the game. The grid clears and symbols drop in. If 3 or more of the same symbols are connected side-to-side or above-and-below, they form a cluster of symbols, disappear from the grid, and award the corresponding prize. More symbols drop into the grid to fill the empty spaces.
The Wild Octopus Symbol can appear within the symbol cluster and transform to match the connected symbols. The Wild Octopus Symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Luckly Fish Bubble.
Collect 3 Lucky Fish Bubble Symbols to trigger the Lucky Fish Bonus.
Symbols cannot be connected diagonally to form a cluster.

Lucky Fish Bonus
Triggering the Lucky Fish Bonus awards 5 bonus rounds and randomly assigns a Lucky Fish, with a unique pattern, shape, and color.
For each round, a new fish appears. If a pattern, shape, or color of the new fish matches the Lucky Fish, a multiplier is awarded:
â€¢ Pattern match â€“ 2x multiplier
â€¢ Shape match â€“ 3x multiplier
â€¢ Color match â€“ 4x multiplier
Within a round, awarded multiplier values are multiplied together to create a total multiplier value. For example, if 2x and 3x multipliers are awarded, the total multiplier value for that round is 6x. Multipliers for each round are added together to award a total multiplier value for the Lucky Fish Bonus. The total bonus win is equal to the total multiplier value multiplied by the bet amount.
The bonus cannot be retriggered.

Hot Hit Jackpot Bonus
The secondary, multi-level progressive Hot Hit Jackpot Bonus may be randomly triggered after the base game and any triggered bonus games have completed.
On each spin, the Hot Hit Jackpots meter indicates how close the spin comes to triggering the Hot Hit Jackpot Bonus. When the meter fills completely, the Hot Hit Jackpots Bonus triggers.
The bonus displays 15 Jackpot Symbols. Reveal symbols until 3 matching symbols are uncovered. The jackpot prize associated with that symbol is awarded.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no more clusters are matched or symbols cascade in, and any triggered bonus games are completed.

Listen for the thunderous rush of the elephant in Elephant King and big wins are sure to follow! Collect clusters of matching, adjacent symbols to win prizes. Watch for the Prize Disk feature to award you instant prizes, trigger the Free Turns Bonus, or award a Mega, Major, or Mini Jackpot!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Collect clusters of matching, adjacent symbols to win prizes.
When 3 or more identical symbols are connected and share a side in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize and is removed from the grid.
Additional symbols cascade down to fill the grid. These symbols can create new clusters, which award prizes and are removed from the grid. This process continues until no new clusters form.
The game continues until no winning clusters remain on the grid and all prizes have been awarded.
If triggered, the Progressive Jackpot amount is awarded in lieu of any other prizes.

Wild Symbols
Wild Symbols can substitute for all cluster symbols. Wild Symbols can help create or enhance clusters, but only apply when they are part of a winning cluster.

Prize Disk Feature
The Prize Disk feature can award instant win prizes, trigger the Free Turns Bonus, or award a Mega, Major, or Mini Jackpot.
If a Prize Disk Symbol lands on the play grid, the prize directly above that column, on the Prize Disk row, is awarded instantly.
If a Prize Disk Symbol lands where there is a Jackpot symbol in the triggering position of the Prize Disk row, the Mega, Major, or Mini Jackpot is awarded.
If a Prize Disk Symbol lands where the Free Turns Symbol is in the triggering position of the Prize Disk row, the Free Turns Bonus is awarded.

Free Turns Bonus
The Free Turns Bonus awards 10 free turns.
Game play in the bonus is similar to the base game, where each turn may create winning clusters with matching symbols.
During the bonus, the prizes in the Prize Disk row shift one position to the left, introducing a new award in the position over the 5th column.
All prizes of the 4 highest cluster symbols are doubled throughout the bonus.
If a Prize Disk Symbol lands where the Extra Turns Symbol appears in the triggering position of the Prize Disk row, 2 extra Free Turns are awarded.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no clusters remain on the grid and any bonus games are completed.

Classic fruit symbol action gets wild in Super Star Fruits! Collect clusters of matching symbols to win prizes. When a Multiplier Wild Symbol appears, it can help to form clusters and award a multiplier up to 50x! Star light, star brightâ€¦will I see big wins tonight?

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Collect clusters of 4 or more matching, adjacent symbols to win a prize. Winning clusters are removed from the play grid and replaced with new symbols.
The game continues until no winning clusters remain on the grid.

Multiplier Wild Symbols
Multiplier Wild Symbols may drop on the grid, offering multipliers from 2x to 50x and helping to create clusters.
If a Multiplier Wild Symbol is part of a winning cluster, the multiplier is applied to the prize.
More than 1 Multiplier Wild Symbol can be applied to a cluster prize.
Multiplier Wild Symbols do not tumble or change position.

Oversize Symbols
Oversize Symbols of 2x2 or 3x3 may drop into the grid and award a prize.
If a 2x2 Oversize Symbol drops in, it transforms into 4 individual symbols and awards the corresponding prize.
If a 3x3 Oversize Symbol drops in, it transforms into 9 individual symbols and awards the corresponding prize.
If there are any adjacent symbols that match the Oversize Symbol when it drops in, those symbols are added to the cluster and the corresponding prize is awarded.

Bonus
The Bonus is triggered when 3 Multiplier Wild Symbols drop into the grid at the same time and awards 8 free turns.
The Bonus play grid is the same as the main game.
The 3 Multiplier Wild Symbols that triggered the Bonus lock into position and remain in place for the duration of the Bonus.
Oversize Symbols are available in the Bonus.
Additional Multiplier Wild Symbols may drop in during the Bonus.
Each additional Multiplier Wild symbol that drops in locks into place for the duration of the Bonus and awards +2 free turns.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no winning clusters remain on the grid and all triggered Bonus games have completed.

Curiouser and curiouser! What whimsical rewards await in Fortunes of Wonderland? Win a prize when you match 3, 4 or 5 symbols across a row. A Wild Symbol might appear in the 4th or 5th columns to improve your win! Trigger the Palace Plinko Bonus or the Soldier Picker Bonus for even more prizes! This fun game will have you grinning like the Cheshire Cat!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Match 3, 4 or 5 of the same symbols across a row to win a prize. The game contains 6 rows, each of which are played individually.

The 4th and 5th symbol of each row are revealed by a spinning symbol. Wild Symbols can appear in the 4th and 5th columns. The Wild Symbol substitutes for all symbols, except Heart Coin Symbols and Soldier Card Symbols, which are bonus-triggering symbols.

Palace Plinko Bonus
Trigger the Palace Plinko Bonus buy collecting 5 or more Heart Coin Symbols across all rows.

The Palace Plinko Bonus features a coin pusher machine. Drop coins into the machine by tapping the slots above the coins. Coins pushed off the edge award prizes.

The number of Heart Coin Symbols collected in the base game is the number of coins that can be dropped in the bonus game.

The bonus ends once all coins have dropped and no further coins will drop off the edge.

Soldier Picker Bonus
Trigger the Soldier Picker Bonus by revealing the Soldier Card Symbol.

Select cards to reveal symbols. Reveal a Heart Symbol to win a prize. Reveal a double Heart Symbol to win double the prize. Reveal a triple Heart Symbol to triple the prize.

The bonus ends once all cards have been revealed.

Completing the Game
The game ends when all symbols have been revealed in the base game and any triggered bonus games have completed.

Reveal All
Press the double-arrow/fast-forward button to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections have been made.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Linked Wins
Linked Wins multiply matched numbers to increase the awarded prize values.
When 2 or more matched numbers are connected side-to-side or above-and-below, those wins are multiplied by the number of connected matches. For example: 2 linked wins are multiplied by 2x, and 3 linked wins are multiplied by 3x. Linked Wins can be multiplied up to 10x.
If an instant win multiplier appears in a Linked Win, the instant win is awarded separately and the remaining Linked Wins are evaluated independently.
Linked Wins cannot be connected diagonally.

Free Turns Bonus
Triggering the Free Turns Bonus awards 5 turns. The game displays a new set of Your Numbers and Winning Numbers.
Linked Wins and instant win multipliers are available in the bonus.
The Free Turns Bonus cannot be retriggered.

Completing the Game

Have a sporting good time as you collect balls to win prizes! Spin the wheel and watch as matching balls fill the prize meters, multipliers are revealed, and extra spins, instant wins, or extra balls are collected!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Each game consists of 6 spins of the wheel. Press SPIN to spin the wheel. On each spin, 3 sections of the wheel spin: an Inner Wheel, Middle Wheel, and Outer Wheel. When the wheel stops, all 3 of the highlighted sections of the wheel are evaluated according to the following:

Outer Wheel â€“ 3 Ball Symbols of varied types, or Trophy Bonus Symbols, are highlighted on the wheel. Each highlighted ball or trophy fills 1 bar on the corresponding prize meter. Fill all bars on the prize meter to win the prize for that ball. Multiple prizes of different balls may be awarded. Each meter can only be won once. Fill all bars on the Trophy Bonus meter to trigger the Bonus game.

Middle Wheel â€“ Awards a 1x, 2x, or 3x ball or trophy multiplier. The multiplier fills the corresponding prize meter for each highlighted ball or trophy on the Outer Wheel by 1, 2, or 3 bars respectively.

Inner Wheel â€“ On each spin, a symbol or blank space is revealed. Possible symbols include:
â€¢    Free Spin Symbol â€“ Adds +1 additional spin to the total remaining spins available
â€¢    Instant Win Symbol â€“ Select 1 of up to 3 Symbols to reveal an instant prize
â€¢    Expand Symbol â€“ Expands the highlighted section of the Outer Wheel, increasing the number of balls or trophies highlighted by 2 for a total of 5

Bonus Game
If all 5 bars on the Trophy Bonus prize meter are filled, the Bonus game plays immediately.

The Bonus game awards 3 initial spins on a 4x4 grid. Any Trophy Symbol that appears on the grid is highlighted and locks into that position on the grid for the remainder of the bonus, and the number of spins remaining is reset to 3 spins. If no Trophy Symbols appear on the grid, the number of spins remaining decreases by 1.

On subsequent spins, any additional Trophy Symbols that appear lock into position for the remainder of the bonus, and are added to the total, and the number of spins resets to 3.

Continue to spin until there are no spins remaining, or all 16 bars on the grid are filled with Trophy Symbols.

If 4 or more symbols are revealed, win the corresponding prize.

At the end of the bonus, the game returns to the base game to complete any spins remaining on the wheel. Only 1 Bonus game may be awarded.

Completing the Game
The game ends after all awarded wheel spins in the base game and any triggered bonus game have completed.

Auto Play
Auto Play is available in both the Base Game and the Bonus Game. Press AUTO SPIN to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all spins have been made.
Press the stop button to continue the game in manual play mode.

The object of the game is to match Your Numbers to Winning Numbers to win a prize.
Reveal Multipliers to win a prize instantly. The available instant win multipliers are 2x, 3x, 5x, 10x, 20x, and 50x.
Reveal a Blue Diamond to trigger the Free Turns Bonus.

Linked Wins

Linked Wins multiply matched numbers to increase the awarded prize values.
When 2 or more matched numbers are connected side-to-side or above-and-below, those wins are multiplied by the number of connected matches. For example: 2 linked wins are multiplied by 2x, and 3 linked wins are multiplied by 3x. Linked Wins can be multiplied up to 10x.

If an instant win multiplier appears in a Linked Win, the instant win is awarded separately, and the remaining Linked Wins are evaluated independently.

Linked Wins cannot be connected diagonally. 

Free Turns Bonus

Triggering the Free Turns Bonus awards 5 turns. The game displays a new set of Your Numbers and Winning Numbers.

Linked Wins and instant win multipliers are available in the bonus.
The Free Turns Bonus cannot be retriggered.

Completing the Game
The game ends when all Winning Numbers and Your Numbers are revealed, and any triggered bonus games are completed.

Press REVEAL ALL to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections have been made.

The Expander Arrow Symbol expands the grid based on revealed arrow patterns. An Expander Symbol performs its action when no more winning clusters remain.

Collect 3 Bonus Symbols to trigger the Love Struck Bonus.

Love Struck Bonus
Click on the tiles to reveal Heart Symbols, a Mystery Instant Win Symbol, or Bonus Win Multiplier Symbols. Press AUTO PLAY to automatically play the bonus game to completion.
Collect Heart Symbols to populate the Heart Meters. Fill a meter to win a prize. Wild Hearts increment all meters.
Find a Mystery Prize Box Symbol to reveal an Instant Win prize.
Reveal a Golden Ticket Symbol to multiply the Bonus Win amount.
The Bonus round continues until a prize is awarded.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no winning clusters remain on the grid, and any triggered bonus games are completed.

Crooks are on the lam with their loot in Run for Riches! Capture thieves as they run across the screen to earn pointsâ€”the faster you tap, the higher the points. You can keep trying until you trigger the Picker game for a chance to win instant prizes and multipliers to increase your rewards.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Capture thieves to earn points and collect selections for the Picker game.

Each thief captured is worth 1 pick in the Picker game. Capture the large sack thief to earn 2 picks in the Picker game! Tapping a policeman reduces the collected thieves amount by 1.

Keep track of your point history with the scoreboard: While playing the base game, each thief that appears on the screen starts with a value of 500 points and reduces in value the longer they stay on the screen. Tap fast to gain the most points. Missing a thief deducts 100 points, and tapping a police officer deducts 500 points. The points are just for fun and donâ€™t have any impact on the prizes won.

Each thief captured removes a handcuff from the box. After 3 taps, press to refill the handcuffs.

Collect 6 or more thieves to trigger the Picker game. Up to 18 money sacks can appear in the Picker game.

If fewer than 6 thieves are captured in the base game, the base game offers another chance to play at no additional cost.

The base game ends after 17 thieves have run across the screen.

Press AUTO to play the base game automatically and proceed to the Picker Game.

Picker Game

Press each money sack in the vault to reveal prize values. Match 3 prize values to win that prize. Three matching money sacks will glow blue.

Revealing an instant win prize awards that prize instantly. Instant-win money sacks will glow pink.

If a multiplier is revealed, any prizes, including instant win prizes, are multiplied by that value and awarded. Multiplier money sacks will glow green.

Press REVEAL ALL to play the Picker game automatically.

Completing the Game

The game ends after 17 thieves have run across the screen in the base game and the triggered Picker game has completed.

Is there treasure in your future? Consult the compass and chart your path to riches in Treasure Cove! Match symbols to win prizesâ€”you could even win the MEGA prize!!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Press each Pirate Flag to reveal a symbol. Reveal 3, 4, or 5 identical symbols to win a prize.

Reveal a Compass Symbol to trigger the Mystery Feature.

Reveal 3 matching Treasure Chest Bonus Symbols to trigger the Multiplier Bonus.

Reveal 3, 4, or 5 Gem Symbols to win a Mini, Major, or Mega Prize.

Mystery Feature

When the Compass Symbol is revealed, it transforms into one of the game symbols, a gem symbol, or a Treasure Chest Bonus Symbol.

A random column, row, or diagonal around the Compass Symbol is highlighted. All the highlighted symbols transform into the same symbol, creating or improving a win.

Multiplier Bonus

Triggering the bonus awards 10 turns.

On each turn, all multiplier cards lock into place and all other symbols re-populate.

If a Treasure Chest Symbol lands, all multipliers are collected for that turn, multiplied by the ticket cost, and added to the total Bonus Win.

If 2 Treasure Chest Symbols land at the same time, all multipliers are collected twice for that turn, multiplied by the ticket cost, and added to the total Bonus Win.

If 3 Treasure Chest Symbols land at the same time, all multipliers are collected three times for that turn, multiplied by the ticket cost, and added to the total Bonus Win.

When the bonus ends, all turn wins are added together and awarded as the total Bonus Win.

Completing the Game

The game ends when all symbols have been revealed and any triggered bonus games have completed.

Auto Play

Press the double-arrow/fast-forward button to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections have been made.

Pack your skis, grab your gloves, and hit the slopes in Emoti Collect Winter Vacation! Collect emoticons to fill prize meters, reveal multipliers, or trigger the Moti Mountain Bonus.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Each game starts with 6 spins of the wheel. Press the Play button to start, and for each subsequent spin.
If the wheel pointer indicates an Emoti Symbol, all corresponding Emoti Symbols on the grid are highlighted.
The Emoti Symbols are added to the corresponding prize meter and then removed from the grid. New Emoti Symbols then tumble in from above.
If a Goggles Emoti Symbol is collected, it reveals 1 of 4 possible mystery features: a 2x prize multiplier, +1 free spin, +1 extra row, or the Moti Mountain Bonus. Up to 2 extra rows may be revealed. 
If the wheel pointer indicates a Snowman Symbol, select 1 of up to 3 Snowman Symbols to reveal an instant prize. On subsequent spins, if the Snowman Symbol is indicated, there is 1 less symbol to choose from. A maximum of 2 instant win prizes may be awarded per game.

Moti Mountain Bonus
In the base game, if a Silver Emoti Symbol appears on the grid behind a collected Goggles Emoti Symbol, the Moti Mountain Bonus launches immediately.
Press the Play Symbol to begin the bonus. 14 Silver Emoti Symbols drop from the top of the mountain, landing on pins and bouncing either left or right down to the next pin. This continues until each Emoti Symbol drops into a prize pot meter of varying colors.
When a prize pot meter is filled, the corresponding color meterâ€™s prize amount is awarded. More than 1 prize pot may be awarded.
At the end of the bonus, the game returns to the base game to complete any spins remaining on the wheel. Only 1 Bonus game may be awarded.

Completing the Game
The game ends after all awarded wheel spins in the base game and any triggered bonus game has completed.

Auto Play
Press the double-arrow/fast-forward button to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections
have been made.
Press STOP to continue the game in manual play mode.

Get ready for a spicy good time with sizzling wins!  In Twice as Spice, collect clusters of matching pepper symbols to win prizes.  Can you handle the heat?



","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Collect clusters of 3 or more matching, adjacent symbols to win a prize.  Winning clusters are removed from the play grid and replaced with new symbols.  Wild Sombrero Symbols can help create clusters.

The game continues until no winning clusters remain on the grid.

Split Symbols

Split symbols count as 2 symbols in one spot.

Hot Sauce Symbols

Hot Sauce Symbols can appear as a single symbol or a split symbol.  These can appear anywhere on the grid and do not need to be in a cluster.

Hot Sauce Symbols award the following:

Â·         â€‹4 Hot Sauce Symbols award 5 free turns.

Â·         5 Hot Sauce Symbols award 10 free turns.

Â·         6 Hot Sauce Symbols award the Hot Prize.

Free Turns Bonus

The Free Turns Bonus is triggered when 4 or 5 Hot Sauce Symbols appear on the play grid.  The bonus awards 5 or 10 Free Turns, depending on the number of triggering Hot Sauce Symbols.

Game play in the bonus is similar to the base game, where each turn may create winning clusters with matching symbols.

Each Free Turn has a multiplier shown on the Multiplier Meter.  The multiplier increases with each Free Turn:

Â·         â€‹For 5 Free Turns, the multiplier climbs to 5x on the 5th turn.

Â·         For 10 Free Turns, the multiplier climbs to 10x on the 10th turn.

The multiplier for the current turn is applied to any cluster wins that are awarded during that turn.

When all free turns have completed, the bonus ends and all multiplied wins from each turn are awarded, in addition to any wins from the base game.

Completing the Game

The game ends when no more winning clusters are formed in the base game and when all turns have completed in any triggered bonus games.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of the game is to tap ducks to earn points and collect selections for the Picker game.

Each duck tapped is worth 1 pick in the Picker game. Tap the fat duck to earn 2 picks in the Picker game! Tapping a pigeon reduces the collected duck amount by 1.

Keep track of your point history with the scoreboard: While playing the base game, each duck that appears on the screen starts with a value of 500 points and reduces in value the longer it stays on the screen. Tap fast to gain the most points. Missing a duck deducts 100 points, and tapping a pigeon deducts 500 points. The points are just for fun and donâ€™t have any impact on the prizes won.

Each duck tapped removes a bread slice from the bread box. After 3 taps, press to refill the bread slices.

Collect 6 or more ducks to trigger the Picker game. Up to 18 ducks can appear in the Picker game.

If fewer than 6 ducks are tapped in the base game, the base game offers another chance to play at no additional cost.

The base game ends after 17 ducks have flown across the screen.

Press AUTO to play the base game automatically and proceed to the Picker game.

Picker Game

Press each duck in the pond to reveal prize values.

Match 3 prize values to win that prize.

Revealing an instant win prize awards that prize instantly.

If a multiplier is revealed, any prizes, including instant win prizes, are multiplied by that value and awarded.

Press REVEAL ALL to play the Picker game automatically.

Completing the Game

The game ends after 17 ducks have flown across the screen in the base game and the triggered Picker game has completed.

The object of the game is to match Your Numbers with Winning Numbers to win a prize.
Press PLAY to start the game. New numbers drop into the Winning Numbers column and the Your Numbers game grid. Match any of Your Numbers to the Winning Numbers and win those prizes.

Vortex Swap

If a Vortex Swap Symbol appears, the corresponding prize is awarded instantly. The vortex may also transform up to 3 additional numbers or symbols into instant win prizes.

Rocket Picker Bonus
If the Red, Blue, and Green Rocket Symbols all appear, the Rocket Picker Bonus is activated. Pick 1 of the rockets to reveal a prize.

Planet Bonus
If 3 Bonus Planet Symbols appear in the grid, the Planet Bonus is activated. The Planet Bonus begins with 5 turns. Match a pair of symbols to win a prize.
When symbols match on a turn, multipliers are added to the next turn and increase as more matches are made. The available multiplier values are 2x, 3x, 5x and 10x.

Completing the Game
The game ends when all symbols have cascaded into the play grid, all prizes have been awarded, and any triggered bonus games have completed.

Reveal All

Beachy Bonus

The Beachy Bonus game ends when 16 Fruit Drink Glass symbols are collected or if no Fruit Drink Glass symbols appear for 3 consecutive spins. Only 1 Beachy Bonus game may be awarded.

Experience the luck of the Irish in a fun number-match gameâ€”Lucky 7â€™s Multiplier! Enjoy the big-win potential of multipliersâ€”you could double or triple your prize!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

Match Your Numbers to Winning Numbers and win a prize. There are 8 individual games within each play to match numbers.

If 2 numbers in a game match Winning Numbers, the total prize in that game is doubled. If 3 numbers in a game match Winning Numbers, the total prize in that game is tripled.

If a Lucky 7 Symbol is revealed, all 3 symbols in the game turn into winning symbols, and the total prize in that game is tripled!

Reveal 3 Horseshoe Symbols anywhere in the 8 games to trigger the guaranteed-win Eliminator Bonus.

Eliminator Bonus

The Eliminator Bonus starts with a spinning wheel and a variety of number sets â€“ each set of numbers is associated with a different prize. The bonus round includes 6 turns to spin the wheel. Press the wheel to start the bonus. The wheel spins automatically for the duration of the bonus.

When the wheel stops spinning, the pointer lands on a number, a multiplier, or a blank space in the outer wheel. If the pointer lands on a number, any number sets containing that number are eliminated. If the pointer lands on a multiplier, the total bonus multiplier is increased by that number. If the pointer lands on a space in the inner wheel that has a +1 Symbol, an extra turn to spin the wheel is added.

More than 1 prize may be awarded in the bonus.

Completing the Game
The game ends when all numbers and symbols have been revealed, and any bonus games have completed.

Reveal All
Press REVEAL ALL to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections have been made.
Press STOP to continue the game in manual play mode.

Trawl the sea for big wins when you play Coastal Clusters! Collect clusters of symbols to win prizes. You might even collect enough to earn more free turns! Match fish symbols in the Symbol Match Bonus to earn prizes and multipliersâ€”up to 10x! Good things come to those who bait!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Coastal Clusters is to collect clusters of matching, adjacent symbols to win prizes.
When 3 or more identical symbols are connected and share a side in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize and is removed from the grid. Additional symbols cascade down to fill the grid. These symbols can create new clusters, which award prizes and are removed from the grid. This process continues until no new clusters form. Winning symbols may appear as a large 2x2 symbol to create larger clusters.
A Wild Symbol may appear and form a cluster with any other symbol.
When a Bonus or Free Turn Symbol drops into the grid, it is removed, populates the corresponding me-ter, and is replaced by a new symbol.

Free Turns
When 3 Free Turns Symbols are collected in the Free Turns Meter, 3 to 5 free turns are awarded.

Symbol Match Bonus
When 3 Bonus Symbols are collected in the Bonus Meter, the Symbol Match Bonus is triggered and awards 5 turns.
The bonus displays 2 rows of fish symbols. The top row shows fish in small circles with a prize value. The bottom row shows fish in large circles. The fish symbols spin for each turn.
Match a pair of symbols to win the displayed prize. Multipliers are added to the next turn of any matches and increase as more matches are made. The available multiplier values are, 2x, 3x, 5x, and 10x.
The bonus ends when all 5 turns are completed.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no clusters remain on the grid and all bonus games are completed.
Press the win message to view the gameâ€™s outcome.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of the game is to match 3, 4, or 5 of the same symbols across a row to win. The game contains 6 rows, each of which are played individually.
The first 4 symbols of each row are hidden and are revealed manually by selecting the row or by pressing REVEAL ALL.
The 5th symbol of each row is revealed by a spinning column, which stops once all other symbols have been revealed.
A Wild symbol can appear in the spinning column and cover 1 to 6 rows. The Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Bonus Coin.
The Coin Dozer Bonus is triggered by collecting 5 or more Bonus Coin symbols across all rows.

Coin Dozer Bonus
The Coin Dozer Bonus features a coin pusher machine. Drop coins into the machine by tapping the bar above the coins. Coins pushed off the edge award additional prizes.
The number of Bonus Coins collected in the main game are the number of Bonus Coins available to drop within the bonus game.
A Nudge may also be awarded in the bonus game. The Nudge shakes the machine, causing more coins to fall off the edge, awarding additional prizes.
The bonus ends once all coins have dropped and no further nudge is awarded.
The game ends after all symbols are revealed and the bonus game has finished. A message appears indicating the gameâ€™s outcome.

  • Outer Wheel â€“3 emoticons of varied colors are highlighted on the wheel. Each highlighted emoticon fills 1 bar on the corresponding-colored prize meter.

  • Inner Wheel â€“ On each spin, 1 of 3 items may be awarded:
    • Free Spin Symbol â€“ Adds +1 additional spin to the total remaining spins available.
    • Instant Win Symbol â€“ Select 1 of up to 3 Symbols to reveal an instant prize.
    • Expand Symbol â€“ Expands the highlighted section of the Outer Wheel, increasing the number of emoticons highlighted by 2 for a total of 5 emoticons.

Fill a prize meter to win the prize for that color. Multiple prizes of different colors may be awarded.  Each meter can only be won once.

Bonus Game

If all 5 bars on the Bonus prize meter are filled, the Bonus game plays immediately.

The Bonus game awards 3 initial spins on a 4x4 grid. Any Bonus Symbol that appears on the grid is highlighted and locks into position on the grid for the remainder of the bonus, and the number of spins remaining is reset to 3. If no Bonus Symbols appear on the grid, the number of spins remaining decreases by 1.

Continue to spin until there are no spins remaining, or all 16 positions on the grid are filled with Bonus Symbols. If 4 or more Bonus Symbols are revealed, win the corresponding prize.

At the end of the bonus, the game returns to the base game to complete any spins remaining on the wheel. Only 1 Bonus game may be awarded.

The game ends when all base game spins and any bonus games are completed, and all prizes have been awarded. A message appears indicating the gameâ€™s outcome.

Rock on! Itâ€™s a screaming good time in the mosh pit when you play Fortunes of Rock! Collect clusters of symbols to win prizes. You might even collect enough to earn more free turns!


","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"


The object of Fortunes of Rock is to collect clusters of matching, adjacent symbols to win prizes.

When 3 or more identical symbols are connected and share a side in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize and is removed from the grid. Additional symbols cascade down to fill the grid. These symbols can create new clusters, which award prizes and are removed from the grid. This process continues until no new clusters form. Winning symbols may appear as a large 2x2 symbol to create larger clusters.


A Wild Symbol, shown as an amplifier, may appear and can take the place of any non-Bonus symbol on the grid to form a cluster.

When a Bonus or Free Turn Symbol drops into the grid, it is removed, populates the corresponding meter, and is replaced by a new symbol.

Free Turns Bonus

When 3 Free Turns Symbols, shown as a microphone, are collected in the Free Turns Meter, 3 to 5 free turns are awarded.

Symbol Match Bonus

When 3 Bonus Symbols, shown as a gold record, are collected in the Bonus Meter, the Symbol Match Bonus game is triggered and awards 5 turns.

The bonus game displays 2 rows of symbols. The top row shows symbols in small circles with a prize value. The bottom row shows symbols in large circles. The symbols spin for each turn.

Match the symbol in the top row to the symbol directly beneath it to win the displayed prize. If a Multiplier displays on a match, the multiplied prize value is added to the Bonus Total Win display. If a match is made, the Multiplier for that space will increase in the next turn, and will continue to increase if more matches are made. The available multiplier values are, 2x, 3x, 5x, and 10x.

The bonus ends when all 5 turns are completed.

Completing the Game

The game ends when no clusters remain on the grid and all bonus games are completed.

Auto Play
Press AUTO PLAY to automatically play the game to completion. Game play continues until all selections have been made.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Dragon Spawn is to collect clusters of matching, adjacent symbols to win prizes.
When 3 or more identical Dragon Egg Symbols or Elements Symbols are connected in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize and is removed from the grid. Additional symbols cascade down to fill the grid. These symbols can create new clusters, which award prizes and are removed from the grid. This process continues until no new clusters form.

Instant Win Picker Bonus

Reveal 3 Dragon Chests anywhere on the grid to trigger the Instant Win Picker Bonus. Select 1 of 3 chests to reveal a prize.

Free Turns Bonus

Reveal 3 Dragon Ring Symbols anywhere on the grid to trigger 3 Free Turns with Sticking Wilds. Clusters continue to form, award prizes, and are then removed from the grid. During the Free Turns Bonus, Sticking Wilds Symbols appear in the grid. Sticking Wilds remain in place and do not cascade. On the next turn, the Sticking Wilds appear in different positions on the grid. The first free play contains 1 Sticking Wild Symbol, the second free play contains 2 Sticking Wild Symbols, and the third free play contains 3 Sticking Wild Symbols.

Battle Bonus

Reveal the Lock and Key Symbols anywhere on the grid to activate the Battle Bonus. Choose a door to start the bonus.

The Battle Bonus consists of 3 rounds, where 2 dragons are battling each other with spells. Each spell reduces the amount of energy in the dragons' health meters. In each round, the dragons alternate turns and try to deplete the otherâ€™s health meter.
In rounds 1 and 3, the playerâ€™s dragon goes first. In round 2, the opposing dragon goes first. For each round won, the playerâ€™s dragon health meter fills with the remaining energy from that round. For each round lost, the opponentâ€™s health meter fills. The Battle Bonus concludes after 3 rounds, or if the playerâ€™s or opponentâ€™s dragon health meter has completely filled, and all prizes are awarded. 

The game ends when no clusters remain on the grid and all bonus games are completed.

May all your wishes come true in Emoti Collect Shooting Stars! Collect clusters of matching emoji characters to win prizes. Reveal 3 Bonus Symbols to trigger the guaranteed-win Shooting Stars Bonus game!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of EmotiCollect Shooting Stars is to collect clusters of 3 or more matching, adjacent symbols to win a prize. Winning clusters are removed from the play grid and replaced with new symbols. Wild symbols can help create clusters.

The Expander Arrow Symbol expands the grid based on revealed arrow patterns. An Expander Symbol performs its action when no more winning clusters remain.
The game continues until no winning clusters remain on the grid.

Shooting Stars Bonus Game
Collect 3 Bonus Symbols to trigger the guaranteed-win Bonus Game. 
Click on the tiles to reveal Star Symbols, a Mystery Instant Win Symbol, or Bonus Win Multiplier Symbols.
Collect Star Symbols to populate the Star Meters. Fill a meter to win a prize. Wild Stars increment all meters, and the bonus game continues until at least one of the star meters is full.
Find a Mystery Trophy Symbol to reveal an Instant Win prize.
Reveal a Golden Ticket Symbol to multiply the Bonus Win amount.

Completing the Game
The game ends when no winning clusters remain on the grid, and any triggered bonus games are completed.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Little Green Men Warp Reactor is to collect 10, 13, or 16 identical planets to win a prize!

At the start of the game, Little Green Men displays a grid with planets; prize meters for planets, UFOs, and asteroids; and a Play button. To begin, the player selects Play, and the game plays out automatically.

When 3 or more identical planets are adjacent in the grid, they create clusters. The clusters are removed from the grid and the count for each planet increases accordingly in the prize meter. Adjacent planets fill the empty space and new planets fall from above to replenish the grid. Collect at least 10 of any planet to win a prize. Collect 13 or 16 of any planet to win higher prizes.

Collect 4 UFOs to trigger the Warp Bonus and collect additional planets or collect a Star symbol to win a prize instantly.

Collect 4 asteroids to trigger the Whirl Bonus. Planets may change position on the grid, where they may form new clusters to be collected.

A bonus game is triggered only when no clusters remain on the grid.

Play ends when no clusters remain on the grid and all the bonuses are completed. A message appears indicating the gameâ€™s outcome.

Grab your wand and step into the magical world of Prize Potions! Collect clusters of potions and ingredients to win prizes. Crystal ball, treasure chest, and lock and key symbols unlock 3 different Bonus games.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Prize Potions is to collect matching Potion Symbols and Ingredient Symbols.

When 3 or more identical Potion Symbols or Ingredient Symbols are connected by 1 side in the grid, they create clusters. Each cluster awards a prize, and the connected symbols are removed from the grid. Additional symbols cascade down to fill the grid. These symbols can create new clusters to award more prizes and then be removed from the grid. This process continues until no new clusters form.

Free Turns Bonus

Reveal 3 Crystal Ball Symbols anywhere on the grid to trigger the Free Turns Bonus. The Free Turns Bonus consists of 3 free turns. As clusters are formed, prizes are awarded, and the symbols are removed from the grid.

During the Free Turns Bonus, Sticking Wilds appear in the grid and remain in place for the duration of the turn. On the next turn, the Sticking Wilds appear in different positions on the grid. The first free turn contains 1 Sticking Wild Symbol, the second free turn contains 2 Sticking Wild Symbols, and the third free turn contains 3 Sticking Wild Symbols on the grid.

Instant Win Picker Bonus

Reveal 3 Chest Symbols anywhere on the grid to trigger the Instant Win Picker Bonus. Select 1 of 3 Chests to reveal an instant prize.

Potion-Punch Bonus

Reveal both the Key and Lock Symbols anywhere on the grid to trigger the Potion-Punch Bonus. The Potion-Punch Bonus consists of 3 rounds where the playerâ€™s character and the opponent battle. Select 1 of 3 doors to start the bonus.

At the start of each round, each character has an energy meter containing 6 segments. In each round, the characters take alternating turns, trying to deplete the otherâ€™s energy meter. This process continues until one of the meters is empty. The remaining energy in the winning characterâ€™s meter is added to the characterâ€™s collection pot. At the end of the third round, a prize is awarded based on the number of segments filled in the playerâ€™s collection pot.

The game ends when no clusters remain on the grid and all bonus games are completed. A message appears indicating the gameâ€™s outcome.

The 3 outer discs displays letters and the inner disc has 7 circular depressions, one containing a pink diamond.

Press Stop to stop the spinning discs. The 3 letters that display when the discs stop appear in the Your Letters section. If the pink diamond aligns with the 3 letters, a bonus letter is awarded and appears in the Bonus Letters section. The matching letters on the crossword grid are highlighted after each letter is revealed.

Toggle on the Hints button to reveal letters that match. Toggle on the Auto Mark button to automatically highlight matching letters on the grid. Press Auto Play to play the game to completion automatically.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Triple Platinum is to find Platinum Bar or Platinum Ring symbols.
At the start of the game, Triple Platinum displays a grid of 20 gemstone symbols. Press each gemstone to reveal a symbol, or press REVEAL ALL to play the game to completion automatically.
Reveal a single Platinum Bar symbol to win the corresponding prize. Reveal a double Platinum Bar symbol to win double the corresponding prize. Reveal a triple Platinum Bar symbol to win triple the corresponding prize. Reveal 3 or more Bonus Platinum Ring symbols to enter the Bonus round.
Within the Bonus round, the wheel can land on the following items:
-    A prize amount, which banks that prize,
-    An arrow, which proceeds to the next prize wheel,
-    An X, which removes 1 Platinum Ring from the collection
The Bonus ends when no more Platinum Rings remain.
Play ends when all symbols have been revealed, Bonus is complete, and all prizes are awarded. A message appears indicating the game's outcome.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Raining Cash is to match Your Numbers to the Lucky Numbers, reveal an instant win symbol or reveal a Bonus game symbol to enter the bonus.

At the start of the game, Raining Cash displays 5 shields in the Lucky Numbers section and 25 golden moneybags in the Your Numbers section. Press each one to reveal a number or symbol.

Press REVEAL ALL to play automatically.

Match Your Numbers to a Lucky Number to win a prize. Reveal a Gold Bar symbol to win the corresponding prize. Reveal a 2x Gold Bar symbol to win double the corresponding prize. Reveal a Wheel Bonus or Prize Bonus symbol to enter the Bonus round.


Wheel Bonus: Revealing the Wheel Bonus icon in the base game awards the Wheel Bonus game.

Press the spin button. 2 wheels will spin. The inner wheel allocates a prize and the outer wheel allocates the prize multiplier.

Prize Bonus: Revealing the Prize Bonus icon in the base game awards the Prize Bonus game.

The Prize Bonus displays 9 Gold Cases. Press the Gold Cases to reveal prizes or the Collect symbol. When the Collect symbol is revealed, the bonus ends and you win the accumulated prize shown.

Play ends when all symbols have been revealed, all bonus games are complete, and all prizes are awarded. A message appears, indicating the game's outcome.

Place your bets and watch the noble steeds race down the track in Thoroughbred Bucks! Will your horse be the big winner? Take a victory lap in the Bonus Game, where youâ€™re awarded 10 jumps and the chance to win both cash prizes and multipliers. Get ready for a profitable day at the races!

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The race starts with 8 horses. 5 horses are assigned prizes. Each game purchased has 6 turns. Press GO! to start the first turn, then press NEXT TURN to play each following turn. Or press REVEAL ALL to have the game played automatically.

Chevrons appear on the lanes to indicate a horseâ€™s progression to the front position. Single, double, or triple chevrons may appear to symbolize 1, 2, or 3moves forward.

Special items may appear down the lanes:
â€¢ If an Instant Win Symbol is revealed, the prize is awarded instantly.
â€¢ If a Lane Multiplier appears, the specific horseâ€™s prize in that lane is doubled. Up to 3 Lane Multipliers can be awarded per lane in a single game. Each time the multiplier appears, it doubles the current prize value.

If a prize is assigned to the horse that wins the race, that prize is awarded.

Collect 5 Horseshoe Bonus Symbols to trigger the Bonus Game. These symbols can be collected across all lanes.

Bonus Game
The Bonus Game is a victory lap with 10 jumps. 

To start, first select your jockey. Then, for each jump, choose which lane to jump or press REVEAL ALL to randomize the selection for all jumps.

A fence with rosettes appears after the lane selection is made. If a rosette is displayed over the selected lane, 1 to 3 prizes are awarded. Prizes include cash awards or multipliers. Any awarded multipliers are added together.

The bonus finishes after all 10 jumps are complete. The final prize amount multiplied by the final multiplier value is awarded.

The game ends when all turns are completed, and the Bonus Game has finished. A message appears indicating the game's outcome.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Deuces Wild is to find Wild 2 symbols or Joker Hat symbols.

At the start of the game, Deuces Wild displays a grid of 20 card suit symbols (club, heart, spade or diamond). Select a playing-card suit symbol to reveal one of the following:

  • Playing card symbol and a prize value,
  • Single, Double, or Triple Wild 2s symbol and a prize value,
  • a Joker Hat symbol.

Find a Single Wild 2 symbol and win the corresponding prize.  Reveal a Double Wild 2 symbol to win double the corresponding prize.  Reveal a Triple Wild 2 symbol to win triple the corresponding prize.

Reveal 3 or more Joker Hat symbols to enter the Bonus round. Within the bonus round, the wheel can land on the following items:

-        A prize amount, which banks that prize,

-        An arrow, which proceeds to the inner wheel,

-        An X, which removes 1 Joker Hat from the collection.

The Bonus ends when no more Joker Hats remain.

Play ends when all symbols have been revealed, bonus games are complete, and all prizes have been awarded. A message appears indicating the game's outcome.

5 Card Poker

features multiple ways to win. Match Your Hands to Prize Hands to win instantly. Find the Golden Chip to trigger the Lucky Suits Bonus where you choose your own lucky suit! Each game ends with the Lucky Hand draw for another chance at prizes!



","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of 5 Card Poker is to match Your Hands to Prize Hands, reveal a Bonus game symbol to enter the bonus, or match cards in Your Hands to cards in the Lucky Hand.

At the start of the game, 5 Card Poker displays 6 sets of Your Hands, consisting of 5 cards each.

Press each set of 5 cards in Your Hands to reveal the cards in each hand, or click REVEAL ALL to play the game to completion automatically. If any of Your Hands match the Prize Hands, win the corresponding prize. Press SHOW PRIZE HANDS to see the different Prize Hands as well as the prizes connected to each Prize Hand.  Prize Hands include Two Pair, Three of a Kind, Straight, Flush, Full House, Four of a Kind, Straight Flush and Royal Flush.  The suit or card numbers represented are examples and may vary. Press HIDE PRIZE HANDS to return to the game.

Reveal a Golden Chip in any of Your Hands to trigger the Lucky Suits Bonus. In the Lucky Suits Bonus, select a suit. Then press each card or select REVEAL ALL. Match 4 or more cards to the chosen suit and win the corresponding prize.

At the end of each game there is another chance to win with the Lucky Hand draw. 5 cards are drawn. Match 2 or more cards in any individual Your Hand to cards in the Lucky Hand to win the corresponding prize.

Play ends when all cards have been revealed, all bonus games have completed, and all prizes have been awarded. A message appears showing the game's outcome.

The object of Glacial Gold is to match the Player Numbers to the Winning Numbers to win the associated prize.
 
At the start of the game, Glacial Gold displays 3 Winning Numbers and 16 Player Numbers and the REVEAL ALL button. Selecting REVEAL ALL has the game play to completion automatically.

Select the Player Numbers icons to reveal numbers to match to the Winning Numbers to win the associated prize.

Reveal a Gold Ice Cube symbol to win the prize shown instantly.

Reveal a Blue Amulet symbol to multiply the prize by 2x, 5x, or 10x.

Reveal a Golden Goblet symbol to win all prizes shown on the game grid.

A Pick Bonus symbol will trigger the Pick Bonus. In the Pick Bonus, select 1 of the Chests to reveal a cash prize.

Find any Wheel Bonus symbol to trigger the corresponding Wheel Bonus. There are 3 variations of the Wheel Bonus: Bronze, Silver, and Gold. Each Wheel Bonus is triggered by its corresponding symbol and has varying prizes, with the Gold Wheel Bonus having the highest prizes. In the Wheel Bonus, press Spin to spin the wheel and win the prize where the pointer stops.

The game ends after all numbers are revealed and any triggered bonus game has completed. A message appears indicating the gameâ€™s outcome.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Tiki-Tac-Toe is to get a line of three matching symbols, either vertically, horizontally, or diagonally.

At the start of the game, Tiki-Tac-Toe displays a three-by-three grid of 9 symbols. Press PLAY to drop in new symbols and play the game to completion.

If three matching symbols appear in a vertical, horizontal, or diagonal line, a prize is awarded. If a Tiki Sun symbol drops in, it substitutes any other prize symbol and awards three extra bonus turns.

Game play is complete when all symbols have dropped into the game, any bonus turns have completed, and all prizes are awarded. A message appears indicating prize amount won for winning games.

","MainFeature":null,"GameInformation":"

The object of Riches of the Runes is to find 4 or more Rainbow gems and win a prize.

At the start of the game, Riches of the Runes displays 15 glowing stone symbols in a grid. Press each glowing stone to reveal a Rainbow Gem or a Green Gem. Or select REVEAL ALL to reveal all Gems automatically. Reveal 4 or more Rainbow Gems to win a prize. Revealing more Rainbow Gems increases the prize amount.

Each revealed symbol may have a Rune sub-symbol or an Amulet sub-symbol.

Collect 4 Rune symbols to trigger the Rune Bonus. In the Rune Bonus, select 4 of 8 stones to reveal a rune. If the revealed rune matches a rune on the portal, a prize or an Amulet symbol is awarded.

Collect 4 Amulet symbols to trigger the Amulet Bonus. In the Amulet Bonus, select an amulet to reveal a multiplier, which is applied to the total win.

Play ends when all symbols are revealed and all bonus games are complete. A message appears indicating the game's outcome.
